but one is missing,

00:01:10.090 --> 00:01:12.859
then we go if we know that energy is conserved,

00:01:12.859 --> 00:01:16.450
then we can check what that missing product
was.

00:01:16.450 --> 00:01:21.749
it's actually a method that's used in particle
physics analysis is to use this missing momentum

00:01:21.749 --> 00:01:22.749
method

00:01:22.749 --> 00:01:25.609
and if you know the decay you're looking for,
